OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784761381
OL,3,CStrabane man denies murdering father-
OL,4,Cof-two
OL,6,FA man has appeared in court and has
OL,7,Fdenied murdering father-of-two Stephen
OL,8,FHolmes in Strabane.
OL,10,FMr Holmes who was 31, died in hospital
OL,11,Ffollowing an assault in a house in the
OL,12,FBeechmount Village area in February
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FThe man accused of his murder appeared
OL,16,Fat Belfast Crown Court on Wednesday.
OL,18,FDylan McCrossan from Beechmount
OL,19,FVillage in Strabane, confirmed his
OL,20,Fidentity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
