FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784761381
OL,3,CStrabane man denies murdering father-
OL,4,Cof-two
OL,6,FThe 33-year old was then charged with
OL,7,Fmurdering Mr Holmes on February 8,
OL,8,F2025 and when asked how he pleaded,
OL,9,FMcCrossan replied "not guilty."
OL,11,FA defence barrister told Madam Justice
OL,12,FMcBride a medic has been engaged to
OL,13,Fcarry out an assessment and report on
OL,14,FMcCrossan.
OL,16,FThe barrister revealed the doctor and
OL,17,FMcCrossan have met twice and that the
OL,18,F"only matter" now delaying the report
OL,19,Fwas that the medic "wants to explore
OL,20,Fthe previous criminal record" of the
OL,21,Faccused.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784761381
OL,3,CStrabane man denies murdering father-
OL,4,Cof-two
OL,6,FHe added that the doctor has
OL,7,F"indicated to us that he will have the
OL,8,Freport with us within a matter of
OL,9,Fweeks once he receives that."
OL,11,FMcCrossan's barrister also told Madam
OL,12,FJustice McBride that once the medical
OL,13,Freport is received, it may have a
OL,14,F"potential knock-on effect in terms of
OL,15,Fthe defence statement".
OL,17,FIn response, a Crown barrister told
OL,18,Fthe Judge that the prosecution "may
OL,19,Fneed" to instruct its own medical
OL,20,Fexpert once the defence report has
OL,21,Fbeen received.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
