PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1784761381
OL,3,CStrabane man denies murdering father-
OL,4,Cof-two
OL,6,FA murder trial is expected to last
OL,7,Fbetween two and three weeks.
OL,9,FDue to the outstanding issues
OL,10,Fincluding medical reports, Madam
OL,11,FJustice McBride said it made no sense
OL,12,Fto set a date for the trial to
OL,13,Fcommence.
OL,15,FShe instead granted a defence request
OL,16,Ffor McCrossan to appear via videolink
OL,17,Ffor a review on September 18, when
OL,18,Fthere was a "possibility" of moving
OL,19,Ftowards setting a date for the trial.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
